inter = {'parent_m': 'AAA_00002', 'print': False, 'strain': 'aaa', 'end':

self.assertDictEqual(merges[1], {'strain': 'aaa', 'end': 88, 'print': False,
    'start': 30, 'parent_p': 'AAA_00001', 'ID': 'inter_0', 'strand': '-',
